          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>When you make a purchase, we collect:</p><ul><li>Name</li><li>Billing and shipping address</li><li>Email address</li><li>Phone number</li><li>Payment details (processed securely via third-party providers — we do not store full card details)</li></ul>",
