        "pp_body_5": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Body",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We use your personal information to:</p><ul><li>Process and fulfil orders</li><li>Provide shipping and delivery updates</li><li>Communicate with you (customer service, order confirmations)</li><li>Screen orders for fraud or risk</li><li>Improve our website, products and marketing</li><li>Send marketing emails and SMS (if you opt in)</li></ul>",
