        "pp_body_6": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Body",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We only share your information with trusted third parties necessary to operate our business, including:</p><ul><li>Shopify (store platform &amp; checkout)</li><li>Payment providers (e.g. Shopify Payments, PayPal)</li><li>Shipping providers (e.g. Australia Post / MyPost Business)</li><li>Klaviyo (email/SMS marketing)</li><li>Advertising platforms (e.g. Meta, Google)</li></ul><p>We do not sell your personal information.</p>",
